  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2f33351c0b6b7ec2344bc3d33b71e873.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With your friends</strong>, enjoy the fun and chaos! Work together, complete missions, make unforgettable memories on your way to a perfect gas station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/18b2c958d9e7cb16fd590bb2f1e4f290.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade and customize your Gas Station</strong> to make it even better! Expand your services, customize them to your style and enjoy more customers and money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/f3233a62d7fab3d6bf69e345d29d9e30.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Providing the best service</strong> to customers is our first duty, and our gasoline is of the best quality, as is our team! Give customers an unforgettable experience and enjoy the good tips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2750a9c33f893fe2ed2bb0d2a6c72040.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not forgetting the convenience store!</strong> Customers will not only fill up gasoline, they want to buy something! Offer them the best products. In the meantime, <strong>don't forget to protect yourself from thieves</strong> (sometimes they don't know a good word for it!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2378a48acd0320da068d787ea617f4e0.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't have to go only one way to success, you can also <strong>do side jobs and earn additional income!</strong> If you're really confident, don't forget to try your luck with scratch cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Yes, sometimes we too feel like dropping everything and opening a gas station!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2f33351c0b6b7ec2344bc3d33b71e873.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/1af0aef721777ac2cca9bab050140c9d.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>With your friends</strong>, enjoy the fun and chaos! Work together, complete missions, make unforgettable memories on your way to a perfect gas station!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/18b2c958d9e7cb16fd590bb2f1e4f290.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=586 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/9917ab50dca0705f8c2b02ce3df249ad.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Upgrade and customize your Gas Station</strong> to make it even better! Expand your services, customize them to your style and enjoy more customers and money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/f3233a62d7fab3d6bf69e345d29d9e30.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2e39e4f39b3df1d8d964db522a5af998.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Providing the best service</strong> to customers is our first duty, and our gasoline is of the best quality, as is our team! Give customers an unforgettable experience and enjoy the good tips!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2750a9c33f893fe2ed2bb0d2a6c72040.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/30be189822c88b3c895649413a238fd2.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not forgetting the convenience store!</strong> Customers will not only fill up gasoline, they want to buy something! Offer them the best products. In the meantime, <strong>don't forget to protect yourself from thieves</strong> (sometimes they don't know a good word for it!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/2378a48acd0320da068d787ea617f4e0.avif?t=1751455284\" width=800 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.poster.avif?t=1751455284\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.webm?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3044440/extras/69039f65a913d96b09caa4953bc2275b.mp4?t=1751455284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You don't have to go only one way to success, you can also <strong>do side jobs and earn additional income!</strong> If you're really confident, don't forget to try your luck with scratch cards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Yes, sometimes we too feel like dropping everything and opening a gas station!</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
